Sample command lines:
./marss2mcpat.py --marss cg.stats --xml_in myxml.xml --cpu_mode total
./mcpat -infile mcpat.xml -print_level 5 -opt_for_clk 1 > mcpat.out

Notes:
- sudo apt-get install gcc-mutlilib g++-multilib python-yaml
- Some performance stats are not recorded for my current MARSS version but they have minnor impact on the final mcpat results. This could be solved by updating MARSS. 
